{"tid":2318852,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"富商楊家誠銅鑼灣酒店遇襲 兩男玻璃杯扑頭後逃去","createTime":"2020-12-09T15:54:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-11T06:00:16.000Z","uid":240362,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"de18ef75bcb531431bc884afdbeb9c805a44ca51","tid":2318852,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T15:54:31.000Z","msg":"昨日（8日）傍晚6時許，警方接獲銅鑼灣告士打道310號柏寧酒店職員報案，指一名60歲姓楊男子及兩名中年男子，在上址大堂因瑣事爭執，其後兩男懷疑分別以玻璃杯及手襲擊姓楊男子，其後逃去。消息指，該名遇襲男子為富商楊家誠。<br />\n<br />\n警方接報到場，經初步調查，案件列襲擊致造成實際身體傷害，交由灣仔警區刑事調查隊第七隊跟進，暫未有人被捕。楊家誠遇襲後頭部受傷，清醒被送往律敦治醫院治理。<br />\n<br />\n兩名施襲者均年約50多歲，分別為約1.7米高，案發時身穿卡其色上衣、深色長褲男子，以及約1.75米高，案發時身穿黑色上衣、黑色長褲男子。警方仍追緝兩人。<br />\n<br />\n富商楊家誠投資股票和賭場起家，2009年收購當時仍在英超的球會伯明翰逾九成股權，成為首位華人英超球會班主。2011年6月，他涉嫌洗黑錢7.2億元，在山頂白加道寓所被捕，至2014年3月罪成，判監6年，去年1月刑滿出獄。出獄前，區域法院在2018年12月曾頒令，充公楊家誠3.38億港元資產。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201209/GTG4VU7I4BHTFI2KUNZUG6JWIQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201209%2FGTG4VU7I4BHTFI2KUNZUG6JWIQ%2F&d=zhjqHwqbwmwTWRz%2FWGYaUKtywrPEU2nSstxgUPIv8k8%3D&h=cd82667f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201209%2FGTG4VU7I4BHTFI2KUNZUG6JWIQ%2F&h=b021816b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201209/GTG4VU7I4BHTFI2KUNZUG6JWIQ/</a>"},{"pid":"6360bf7822f107a0deb5d7a6afe3289a500b254a","tid":2318852,"uid":310867,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T15:55:41.000Z","msg":"玻璃杯扑你個頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"393935c4f02893c9412cd9abc25605a6df06d57d","tid":2318852,"uid":166308,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T15:56:10.000Z","msg":"又話有國安法香港會仲安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49ce75ade32501a2595608a7431f13fc44b1b6c7","tid":2318852,"uid":223741,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T15:56:17.000Z","msg":"咁有錢都中招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"462715a836c1d2d1a72a601f84e7af3dc47c0914","tid":2318852,"uid":33939,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T15:57:19.000Z","msg":"錢多多都遇襲<br />\n國安法<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7faf4b8e09c06a23b12263d32f4d00ae360a0451","tid":2318852,"uid":54486,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T15:58:12.000Z","msg":"1989年，楊家誠到廣東省東莞市，從事不正當骨場舞廳等開發工作。<br />\n<br />\n之後轉任職髮型師，早年曾任職於城中名媛愛光顧的Le Salon。1994年，在尖沙嘴帝苑酒店開設名為「 Vanity 」的髮型屋，其後在新世界酒店（後改稱九龍萬麗酒店，遺址位於現時的K11 MUSEA）開設分店，專做遊客及熟客生意，間中亦會親身落場向闊太提供性服務。"},{"pid":"5da0979984c1cf8377eafdc55b4c4bc36cc0d153","tid":2318852,"uid":164752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T15:58:27.000Z","msg":"who"},{"pid":"c3d713ef265dbfc1a16f32b272cbe00e27bf9bc9","tid":2318852,"uid":335434,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T15:59:42.000Z","msg":"原來唔經唔覺佢已經坐完出咗冊喇 佢呢啲先係典型嘅洗黑錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"815be70b98a285b1885e083b2b94502b02a2ee2b","tid":2318852,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T16:00:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef6454216147825d2d0fef108dc79097f8df4177","tid":2318852,"uid":353267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T16:00:57.000Z","msg":"咁多億身家，去呢啲酒店<br />\n大學啲u女去開房都覺得唔夠豪華<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34b057d7d8fc1c779abc22ee4b52818966b54173","tid":2318852,"uid":83328,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T16:02:57.000Z","msg":"酒杯扑你個頭<br />\n你阿媽話痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecc1827